{
  "title": "tu pauwayan dra puwangaladan",
  "titleCh": "命名的意義",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "早期卑南族的傳統命名方式是由長輩討論決定。若生男孩，就從父輩祖先的名字中尋找。若生女孩，則從母輩祖先的名字中尋找，不會隨意命名。不管父輩母輩，都取自品德好、健康、孝順、有名望、關愛家人與族人者的祖先名字。然而，卑南族人沒有清晰的命名規則。",
      "ab": "na Pinuyumayan kemay kinabulretrenganan driya, an pungalad dra manuden i, amau tu maidraidrangan na pungalad. an mainayan tu walrak i, maya kantu temuwamuwan na kemay kinuinay. an babayan tu walrak i, maya kantu temuwamuwan na kemay kinubabay. adri patateras elra pungalad. kana kinuinay lra, kana kinubabay lra i, maya kana inaba tu kakuwayanan, kana inaba dra dradrek, kana malubis dratu maidraidrangan, kanantu kinatalrimayan dra nirumaenan aw dra drinekalranan. amawna, tayta na Pinuyumayan i, uniyan dra kuretan dra puwangaladan.",
      "order": "1",
